notes.note: A reference to the Sky Yddet and its Final Blow attack from Earthbound Beginnings. Giygas, not fully realizing what an angel is, thinks Pit is like this but for Earthlings. "Gnilhtrae" is Earthling backwards, if you haven't figured that out yet.
This is my favourite line I've written for Giygas. I wrote it the evening of 2023 February 15, by the way.

For the D_magicant line: I have chosen to interpret the Magicant as resembling bedtime stories that Maria used to tell Giygas.

pendingLines.line: SHAMIKO: (I wonder if anyone here has a mind reading power. Hey! Blink twice if you’re hearing this.)
LOTTE: Sorry. I’m going to sing a little bit. I-It allows me to communicate with the spirits in objects.
You…know Porky Minch. Our relation is closer than we thought…
Who do you think Porky got his troops from? His toys? Who do you think fostered his cruelty, played to his cowardice?
Ha! Ath-Yolazsth’s hunger is but a murmur next to the might of our PSI! It’s already over for you, Earthling!
Zhectast… Compared to me, Zhectast is a puppy! Watch, Earthling! It’s already over for you and your world!
